    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "A bag contains 5 red and 3 blue balls. Two are drawn without \nreplacement. Find $P(\\text{both red})$."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Roll two dice. Find $P(\\text{sum} = 8 | \\text{at least one die is 4})$."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "A biased coin has $P(H) = 0.7$. Find the probability of exactly \n4 heads in 6 flips."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "What is $E[X]$ for the sum of three fair dice?"
    },
